Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.67,0:01:43.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha and Kikyo?\NWhy? What's going on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.45,0:01:49.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.82,0:01:50.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.49,0:01:54.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.88,0:02:21.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}How? How can he not avert his eyes?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:24.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:43.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.04,0:02:47.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is the antibiotic\nand this one's an ointment for pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:52.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And... I brought lots of\ngauze and bandages.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.85,0:02:58.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay! I'll be off then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:02:59.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:01.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you going back?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.02,0:03:02.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:05.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I just came to bring\nsome medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.89,0:03:09.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At least make up with Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:11.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was a silly argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.93,0:03:17.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh right, I had a fight with Inuyasha.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:21.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't care how you feel about me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.11,0:03:24.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't let Naraku have you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.11,0:03:28.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only I can protect you from Naraku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:38.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had forgotten all about\nthe argument we had.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:48.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku,\NKagome seemed very depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:54.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. Well, I can guess why\nshe's feeling that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.35,0:04:01.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those lights!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:09.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.93,0:04:17.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, Kagome went back\nto her home again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:18.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:24.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, you were seeing\NKikyo, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:25.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:29.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And Kagome saw the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:30.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.88,0:04:32.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, she saw us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:35.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How could you sneak around like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:38.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:41.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your face looks like the Buddha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:45.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why's your face looking\nso calm and divine?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:08.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That moment, Inuyasha didn't try to\navert his eyes from me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:12.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha tried to tell me something...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.22,0:05:16.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I was afraid to listen\nand ran away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:20.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha had already decided.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:23.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:28.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha and Kikyo hated each other\nbecause of Naraku's deception.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:31.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo followed Inuyasha and died.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.67,0:05:39.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And Naraku who separated them\nis now after Kikyo again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:42.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't care how you feel about me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:45.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't let Naraku have you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:47.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only I can protect you from Naraku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.36,0:05:54.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no place for me between them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:06.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't forget Kikyo, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:10.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, Kagome...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.38,0:06:14.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't see you anymore.\NI mustn't.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:20.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo gave her very life\nfor Inuyasha's sake.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.72,0:06:23.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't compete with that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:28.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't return to Inuyasha.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:54.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha won't come for me anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:03.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But what'll I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:07.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I brought the Sacred Jewel fragments\nback with me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:09.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should return them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:19.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, after I return them,\nit'll be the end of it all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.22,0:07:24.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll return to my normal existence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:44.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She returned so soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:46.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and she hasn't spoken at all\nsince she returned...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.24,0:07:49.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder\nif something happened to Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:52.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:55.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A thumb?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.52,0:07:57.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fool! A man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.35,0:07:58.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:01.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Could she have had an\nargument with Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:04.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ahem, Kagome...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:05.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:08.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Would you like my egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:11.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:12.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,May I be excused?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:17.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Sis...\N- Sota!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.21,0:08:22.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These pickles are nice and crunchy.\NTry some.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.24,0:08:23.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:27.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, no need\nto wash your dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:28.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll do them all together later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:30.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:40.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.76,0:08:41.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Sis...\N- Kago...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:42.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Have a nice day!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.07,0:08:48.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:50.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.41,0:08:53.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aren't you worried about Sis at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:08:59.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These pickles are really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:15.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:18.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,'Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:19.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're out of the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.07,0:09:24.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You had some kind of\nmysterious rash all over your body?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:27.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess we're running out\nof feigned illnesses.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:30.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, never mind that.\NWhatever happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:32.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- Don't act innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:37.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You know, the jealous, rude\nand spoiled guy of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:39.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you split up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:42.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:44.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did I say something I shouldn't have?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:54.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He dropped me flat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:09:59.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome isn't the one\nthat dumped him?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:01.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does that mean... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.61,0:10:05.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That she still loves him?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.61,0:10:08.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I'm really fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:09.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've gotten over him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:11.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes! So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:13.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,don't bring him up again, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:15.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:18.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She doesn't want to be\nreminded 'cuz it hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.46,0:10:21.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- She's scary.\N- Her fake smile is scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.13,0:10:26.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:29.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:33.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You were so upset because\NKagome got friendly with Koga...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.91,0:10:37.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,yet now, you want to\nthink only about Kikyo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.51,0:10:39.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How shallow your feelings were!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:42.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, go see Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.58,0:10:43.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop it, will ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.05,0:10:46.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've decided not to see her again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:50.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop misunderstanding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.63,0:10:53.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome took Sacred Jewel\nfragments with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.39,0:10:55.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm telling you to go get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:57.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Only you can pass through the well!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.77,0:10:59.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just the Sacred Jewel fragments?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:01.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you care about Kagome?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:07.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.\NInuyasha picked Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:11.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's cruel to ask Kagome\nto come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:15.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:18.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you really sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.75,0:11:21.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What, Kaede?! Not you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:26.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The present Kikyo is made\nfrom earth and bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:30.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's not of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:34.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Kikyo's spirit still remains.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:36.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:39.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You two can never be together\nin this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.21,0:11:44.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister Kikyo's wish is for the\ntwo of you to die together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:49.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fine... I'll go to hell with Kikyo,\nas she wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:55.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If that's my destiny with Kikyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:10.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must go to return\nthe Sacred Jewel fragments.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:17.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I don't want to. I'm afraid!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:21.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once I give this back,\NI won't be able to see Inuyasha again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:24.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry, Kagome.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:26.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to Kikyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.82,0:12:29.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't tell me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:31.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.53,0:12:33.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:38.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish Kikyo would just disappear!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:50.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have... Have I turned into\nsuch a horrible woman?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:57.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I... I probably have a horrible\nlook on my face right now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:01.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't see Inuyasha\nlooking like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.03,0:13:12.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The fragments...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.31,0:13:24.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sacred tree...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.38,0:13:29.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes... This tree...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.82,0:13:33.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the tree on which\NInuyasha was sealed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.86,0:13:36.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Five hundred years ago...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:40.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}this is where I first\nmet Inuyasha.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:43.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's that confused look\non your face, Kikyo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:47.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, are you satisfied, Miss Kikyo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:52.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do it with one shot, will ya?\NLike the time you killed me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.21,0:13:56.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Say, you keep calling me\NKikyo, Kikyo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.91,0:13:59.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let me tell you, my name is...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:04.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:07.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:11.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:16.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:27.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did I ever meet him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:31.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If it were going to hurt this much...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.15,0:14:33.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish I had never met him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:37.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I want to see him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:42.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to see Inuyasha once more!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:51.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...l'm in love with Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:58.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before I knew it,\NI had grown to love him so much!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:08.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.59,0:15:14.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:20.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:34.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:36.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.18,0:15:41.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When you're close to this sacred tree\ndon't you feel a strange power?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.28,0:15:44.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As though you feel more\ntrue to yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.19,0:15:48.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,like your heart feels much more pure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:54.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is where\nyour father proposed to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.50,0:15:55.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.96,0:15:58.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Of course, I loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.30,0:16:02.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But the day before,\nwe had argued over something silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:06.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wasn't sure\nif we could make a go of it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:10.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The moment I walked under this tree\NI felt things clearing up inside me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:12.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and I accepted his proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:16.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And because I did,\NI was able to have you and Sota.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.48,0:16:18.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm grateful to this tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.49,0:16:26.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't ask what's troubling you.\NBut I have faith in you, Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.43,0:16:31.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That you are a child who will choose\nthe path that you believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:35.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:42.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:45.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up! I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:46.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I haven't said a word yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:49.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're gonna tell me\nto go see Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:51.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you know that, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:56.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that'll mean saying\ngoodbye to Kagome.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.69,0:16:59.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Saying something I couldn't\nsay the last time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:01.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll have to this time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:05.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're not the one who's\nhaving a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:07.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:10.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku is absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.77,0:17:14.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've already made up\nyour mind, so fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.31,0:17:17.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But Kagome is probably\nso confused right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.65,0:17:20.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you're a man,\nyou'll go to see Kagome...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:22.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and make a nice, clean break.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:26.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll say... instead of dallying\naround forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.22,0:17:30.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you want me to split\nup with Kagome that much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:32.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you want to split up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.79,0:17:36.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who... Who said that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.77,0:17:40.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I decided to protect Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:43.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So how can I ask Kagome\nto come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.61,0:17:45.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where is everybody?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.14,0:17:50.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Boy, what a poor sport!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:52.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll call him "Two-Faced"\nfrom now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:54.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Gotta keep things together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:17:57.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:05.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nope... I can't ask her\nto come back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.79,0:18:08.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome knows that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:11.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:13.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must see her\nand bid her farewell.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.14,0:18:16.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Otherwise I can't go{\i0} on...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:28.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:41.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,While I was back over there,\NI gave it a lot of thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:45.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,About you and Kikyo and... me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:48.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:50.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.04,0:18:53.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:55.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So I thought I couldn't stay\nhere with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:58.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:02.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Until I met you,\NI never trusted a soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.42,0:19:05.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But... you cried for my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:07.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You always stayed by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:11.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When I'm with you, I'm happy.\NYou soothe my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:12.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:16.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not supposed to be\nhappy and have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:17.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:20.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo followed me in death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:25.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I must repay her with my death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.87,0:19:30.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know. I can't compete with Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.34,0:19:33.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Because... I'm still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.12,0:19:39.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've thought a lot about Kikyo, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:42.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo and I are so different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.19,0:19:45.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even the talk that I'm a\nreincarnation of Kikyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.76,0:19:49.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I'm not Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:52.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My heart belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:57.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I've come to understand\none thing about how Kikyo feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:19:59.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Something she and I share.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:03.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The desire to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:04.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:12.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When I realized that Kikyo and I\nfelt the same thing, I felt a bit better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:17.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The desire to see you is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:21.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why I conjured up the courage\nto come and see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:26.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome...l've wanted to see you, too.\NBut...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:32.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want to stay with you, Inuyasha.\NI can't forget you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:50.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome... How am I to answer you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.26,0:20:52.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.09,0:20:54.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can I ask you one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.71,0:21:06.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will you let me stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.04,0:21:11.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'll stay with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:14.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.68,0:21:19.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can never break the bond\nbetween Inuyasha and Kikyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.85,0:21:21.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I understand that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.69,0:21:25.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Inuyasha...\NI realized this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:29.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My meeting you was no coincidence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:34.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want you to live, Inuyasha.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:38.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:42.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.98,0:21:43.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.18,0:21:47.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want you to be happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:51.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want you to laugh a lot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.06,0:22:03.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know\nwhat I'll be able to do for you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.33,0:22:09.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I'll always stay by your side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.40,0:23:50.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku finds himself under the\ncare of a kind old couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.37,0:23:53.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But a demon attacks him...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.44,0:23:56.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,intent on stealing the Sacred Jewel\nfragment on his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.44,0:23:58.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We all rush to Kohaku's rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.88,0:24:01.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But he has no memory that he is\nthe son of a demon slayer...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.08,0:24:04.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,or even his sister, Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.02,0:24:07.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why? Is this some trick by Naraku?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.42,0:24:12.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Kohaku's Lost Memory"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.83,0:24:14.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
